text: Interstate 190 may refer to the following Interstate Highways in the United States related to Interstate 90: *Interstate 190 (Illinois), a spur into Chicago's O'Hare International Airport *Interstate 190 (Massachusetts), a spur from Worcester to Leominster *Interstate 190 (New York), a spur into Buffalo and Niagara Falls *Interstate 190 (South Dakota), a spur into downtown Rapid City 90-1 1
title: Interstate 190
